column4: Enhance your decor with this beautiful 11x16 image printed directly onto hardwood that is embellished by the raised grain and knotty features. To round out the rustic look, we frame each piece in lath (your choice of natural brown or black) or choose a painted edge. A sawtooth hanger is attached for easy mounting on the wall or use as a shelf sitter. Truly a statement piece that will age beautifully with a rich patina glow.
